    {
      "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-8051-968a-c1e39d94d0d5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Dropout is a big concern, especially among first-year students who may not be ready for the transition between their previous educational settings to the new ones. The work focuses on exploring first-year students’ exam-taking patterns using layered Markov-Chain probabilistic graphs. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-8051-968a-c1e39d94d0d5",
